# Frontend Overview (Laravel)

## Laravel Frontend Options
Laravel supports:
- Blade + PHP templating
- Livewire (server-driven UI)
- Inertia with React/Vue/Svelte
These allow flexible frontend choices depending on interactivity needs. :contentReference[oaicite:1]{index=1}

## Asset Bundling
Laravel uses Vite by default to bundle CSS/JS assets. :contentReference[oaicite:2]{index=2}

## Rules
- Choose one primary frontend strategy per feature.
- Keep backend logic separate from UI rendering.